@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title La rutare: L2 se schimba, L3 ramane

[Host S\nIP_S\nMAC_S] as S
[Router 1\nMAC_R1a/MAC_R1b] as R1
[Router 2\nMAC_R2a/MAC_R2b] as R2
[Host D\nIP_D\nMAC_D] as D

S --> R1 : Cadru L2:\nMAC_S -> MAC_R1a\nPachet L3:\nIP_S -> IP_D
R1 --> R2 : Cadru L2:\nMAC_R1b -> MAC_R2a\nPachet L3:\nIP_S -> IP_D
R2 --> D : Cadru L2:\nMAC_R2b -> MAC_D\nPachet L3:\nIP_S -> IP_D

note bottom
  IP sursa/destinatie raman identice end-to-end.
  MAC sursa/destinatie reflecta hop-ul curent.
end note
@enduml
